column7: Public Health - Sandoa, Democratic Republic of the Congo (5) Médecins Sans Frontières
column9: The Sandoa health zone, in the province of Lualaba, is under epidemiological surveillance. We fear a measles outbreak that will require a mass vaccination campaign in the coming weeks. The mapping of this vast territory is necessary to support planning the response.
